name: CreateNotebook
description:
Create a new notebook within a specified project.

This tool allows for the creation of a new notebook within a specified project in Datadog. Ideal for organizing data and analyses in one place.

parameters.name: project_identifier
parameters.description: The ID of the project where the notebook will be created. Use /api/projects/ to find the ID.

value_schema.description: Project ID of the project you're trying to access. To find the ID of the project, make a call to /api/projects/.

parameters.name: notebook_details
parameters.description: A JSON object containing details for the new notebook, including id, title, content, and other metadata.

user_access_level.description: The effective access level the user has for this object
